comment: Short predicate calculus proof of the left-to-right implication of ~ dftr4 . A transitive class is a subset of its power class. This proof was constructed by applying Metamath's minimize command to the proof of ~ trsspwALT2 , which is the virtual deduction proof ~ trsspwALT without virtual deductions.
